n/author-LM0kb8TnwF3pXyZ2viD2Eg">Mai Nghiêu Thần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/T%C3%A2n-lang/poem-i3_OT8pP-hlCO0Tgnr_YMw">Tân lang - 檳榔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-v%C5%A9-th%C3%A1n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-FcWzM9R187Ql7EMOYNDoaA">Thu vũ thán kỳ 1 - 秋雨歎其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/Tinh-v%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-U-UdRfLXM-HV5EA5LGqnwg">Tinh vệ từ - 精衛詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-Xw0ALUMVQ06c4vUGFngNbA">Vương Kiến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
